Fortune Brands Reports Accord to Sell Acushnet Golf Unit for $1.23 Billion

-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 
2011-05-20T12:02:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/fortune-brands-reports-accord-to-sell-acushnet-golf-unit-for-1-23-billion.html
Fortune Brands Inc. (FO)  reported an
agreement for the sale of its Acushnet Co. golf business to a
group led by  Fila Korea Ltd. (081660) , the owner of the Fila brand
globally, and Mirae Asset Private Equity. The purchase price is
$1.225 billion in cash.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  